### Overview

This demo uses `infiniteLoop: false` and `hideControlOnEnd: true` to create a manual style that automatically hides controls when at the beginning and end of the slide show.

### Setup
```
$('.bxslider').bxSlider({
  infiniteLoop: false,
  hideControlOnEnd: true
});
```
